CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778595071
OL,3,CWitness denies entering tunnel to
OL,4,Cprove Noah Donohoe could have got out
OL,6,FA senior civil servant has denied that
OL,7,Fhe entered a culvert five years after
OL,8,FNoah Donohoe's body was found in it in
OL,9,Forder to demonstrate the schoolboy
OL,10,Fcould have exited the tunnel.
OL,12,FJonathan McKee from the Department for
OL,13,FInfrastructure (DfI), told Belfast
OL,14,FCoroner's Court that he had gone into
OL,15,Fthe underground tunnel because he
OL,16,Fwanted to be "sure of the facts"
OL,17,Fwhether someone would be able to get
OL,18,Fback out.
OL,26,@xD@NOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
