OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778595071
OL,3,CWitness denies entering tunnel to
OL,4,Cprove Noah Donohoe could have got out
OL,6,FNoah, a pupil at St Malachy's College,
OL,7,Fwas 14 when his naked body was found
OL,8,Fin an underground water tunnel in
OL,9,Fnorth Belfast on June 27 2020, six
OL,10,Fdays after he left home on his bike to
OL,11,Fmeet two friends in the Cavehill area
OL,12,Fof the city.
OL,14,FHe was found more than 600 metres
OL,15,Fdownstream from where he had last been
OL,16,Fseen close to the culvert inlet behind
OL,17,Fhouses at Northwood Road in north
OL,18,FBelfast.
OL,20,FA post-mortem examination found the
OL,21,Flikely cause of death was drowning.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778595071
OL,3,CWitness denies entering tunnel to
OL,4,Cprove Noah Donohoe could have got out
OL,6,FThe long-running inquest, which is in
OL,7,Fits 15th week, heard further evidence
OL,8,Ffrom Mr McKee, a Department for
OL,9,FInfrastructure (DfI) official on
OL,10,FTuesday.
OL,12,FHe was questioned by Brenda Campbell
OL,13,FKC, who represents Fiona Donohoe,
OL,14,FNoah's mother, in the proceedings.
OL,16,FThe barrister asked the witness about
OL,17,Fan approach by police to the
OL,18,Fdepartment asking for information
OL,19,Fabout the Premier Drive culvert while
OL,20,Fthe search for Noah was ongoing in
OL,21,FJune 2020.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778595071
OL,3,CWitness denies entering tunnel to
OL,4,Cprove Noah Donohoe could have got out
OL,6,FMr McKee said police were seeking
OL,7,Fdetails about the culvert layout.
OL,9,FThe witness also told the court that a
OL,10,Fdesilting operation had begun in March
OL,11,F2020 but had been postponed because
OL,12,Fthe silt in the tunnels needed testing
OL,13,Fand then because of the Covid pandemic.
OL,15,FMr McKee said the department had
OL,16,Fbelieved the operation would cost
OL,17,Faround #78,000 to complete, but it
OL,18,Fended up costing #500,000.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778595071
OL,3,CWitness denies entering tunnel to
OL,4,Cprove Noah Donohoe could have got out
OL,6,FThe jury were then shown CCTV footage
OL,7,Ffrom inside the underground water
OL,8,Ftunnel which was recorded in August
OL,9,F2013.
OL,11,FMs Campbell said 15 minutes of footage
OL,12,Fhad been recorded on a single day.
OL,14,FShe said: "Nobody asked the department
OL,15,Ffor the information that they had
OL,16,Favailable to them about how easy it
OL,17,Fwas to search that aspect of the upper
OL,18,Fstretch from the inlet down to the
OL,19,FShore Road while Noah was missing."
OL,26,@vD@KOU{D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778595071
OL,3,CWitness denies entering tunnel to
OL,4,Cprove Noah Donohoe could have got out
OL,6,FMs Campbell then told the jury that
OL,7,Fthe witness had gone into that section
OL,8,Fof the culvert twice in autumn 2025.
OL,10,FShe said: "It has been emphasised to
OL,11,Fus that going into a confined space
OL,12,Freally is a matter of last resort. I
OL,13,Fjust want to understand how and why it
OL,14,Fis you and your colleague took that
OL,15,Fdecision.
OL,17,F"Who asked you to do that?"
OL,19,FMr McKee said: "No-one, I did that of
OL,20,Fmy own choice."
OL,26,@rD@KOUyD@AOUyD@[O]{D@POU|D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778595071
OL,3,CWitness denies entering tunnel to
OL,4,Cprove Noah Donohoe could have got out
OL,6,FThe barrister said Mr McKee had been
OL,7,Fable to crawl from one of the manhole
OL,8,Fentrances to the culvert inlet.
OL,10,FShe added: "Why did the department
OL,11,Fdecide in October 2025 to put
OL,12,Foperatives in and to make that ascent?"
OL,14,FHe said: "The department's view was
OL,15,Fthat if someone got into the culvert,
OL,16,Fthey could easily get out of it.
OL,26,@rD@LOUtD@gO]vD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778595071
OL,3,CWitness denies entering tunnel to
OL,4,Cprove Noah Donohoe could have got out
OL,6,F"In the earlier section of it... it is
OL,7,Fclassified as steep. I wanted to be
OL,8,Fsure that if you were making your way
OL,9,Fout of the culvert, you would be able
OL,10,Fto do so."
OL,12,FMs Campbell continued: "If a child get
OL,13,Fthemselves in, they should get
OL,14,Fthemselves out? Is that the point you
OL,15,Fwere trying to prove?"
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@JO]tD@XOUwD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778595071
OL,3,CWitness denies entering tunnel to
OL,4,Cprove Noah Donohoe could have got out
OL,6,FMr McKee said: "The point I was trying
OL,7,Fto prove is if you were able to make
OL,8,Fyour way down into the culvert and
OL,9,Fthen decided that you wanted to turn
OL,10,Fand come back out again, would you
OL,11,Factually be able to."
OL,13,FMs Campbell added: "If a child gets
OL,14,Fthemselves in there, should they
OL,15,Fshoulder the burden of getting
OL,16,Fthemselves out?"
OL,18,FHe said: "No. I made the survey to be
OL,19,Fsure of the facts, could you actually
OL,20,Fget out of the pipe."
OL,26,@nD@POUsD@UO]uD@TOUxD@PO]zD@JOU|D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778595071
OL,3,CWitness denies entering tunnel to
OL,4,Cprove Noah Donohoe could have got out
OL,6,FThe barrister said the witness had
OL,7,Fmade a second trip into the lower
OL,8,Fsection of the tunnel network in
OL,9,FNovember 2025, which she described as
OL,10,F"the belly of the beast".
OL,12,FMs Campbell said: "Is this so you
OL,13,Fcould tell us that if Noah found
OL,14,Fhimself down there, he could have
OL,15,Fclimbed up a ladder and put his
OL,16,Fshoulder to a manhole and been
OL,17,Fresponsible for getting himself out?"
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@XO]tD@SOUyD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778595071
OL,3,CWitness denies entering tunnel to
OL,4,Cprove Noah Donohoe could have got out
OL,6,FMr McKee responded: "The reason I made
OL,7,Fthe survey in the bottom section was
OL,8,Fbecause others were talking about
OL,9,Flight ingress.
OL,11,F"It wasn't in any way to suggest that
OL,12,Fwith Noah being there, it was up to
OL,13,Fhim to get himself out, not at all.
OL,15,F"It was simply a survey to understand
OL,16,Fthe culvert as well as I could."
OL,18,FThe witness was later questioned about
OL,19,Fa safety review of culverts in
OL,20,FNorthern Ireland carried out following
OL,21,Fthe death of Noah.
OL,26,@nD@UOUsD@AOUwD@AOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778595071
OL,3,CWitness denies entering tunnel to
OL,4,Cprove Noah Donohoe could have got out
OL,6,FThe inquest heard that 270 culvert
OL,7,Fscreens had been removed following the
OL,8,Freview, with 15 debris screens changed
OL,9,Fto security screens.
OL,11,FHe told the court: "We wanted to know
OL,12,Fwhere we are managing our
OL,13,Finfrastructure properly.
OL,15,F"Had we the right type of
OL,16,Finfrastructure in place? A review to
OL,17,Fsee how it weights up against the most
OL,18,Frecent guidance was the best way to do
OL,19,Fthat.
OL,26,@sD@TOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1778595071
OL,3,CWitness denies entering tunnel to
OL,4,Cprove Noah Donohoe could have got out
OL,6,F"We wanted to know had we the right
OL,7,Finfrastructure in place here, and not
OL,8,Fonly here, but in all of our other
OL,9,Fscreen locations.
OL,11,F"Are we getting this right?"
OL,13,FThe inquest continues.
